    "For each phase, the relevant SE keywords are combined using the OR operator to capture all variations.",
    "The final search query for each SDLC phase follows the format: [agent words] AND [SE words].Following the guide of previous work [99,128,168], we design the following inclusion and exclusion criteria.",
    "In the first phase, we filtered out short papers (exclusion criterion 1) and removed duplicates (exclusion criterion 2).",
    "In the second phase, we manually screened each paper's venue, title, and abstract, excluding items such as books, keynote speeches, panel summaries, technical reports, theses, tool demonstrations, editorials, literature reviews, and surveys (exclusion criteria 3 and 4).",
    "In the third phase, we conducted a full-text review to further refine relevant studies."
